ect CFT data, and we discuss various\nexamples, including one-point functions of bulk operators, scaling dimensions\nof defect operators, and four-point functions of operator insertions on the\ndefect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Feb 2021 17:29:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Oct 2021 02:14:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-23"}
