ime, and the random-walk-step duration can be used to\nconstruct temporal scalings which allow for common waiting-time, contact-count,\nand contact-duration distributions across different populations. Semi-analytic\napproximations for both the waiting-time and contact-duration distributions are\nalso presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Feb 2021 23:08:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Jun 2021 21:25:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 1 Sep 2021 21:47:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-12"}
