5 degrees. The simulation results were compared with the\nexperimental emission spectrum, showing a quantitative agreement with the\npredictions provided by our framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 2021 08:31:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Apr 2021 09:21:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 3 May 2021 10:11:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-19"}
