8. They show stratification in temperature\ndistribution with the shape of the high temperature region as in the VLTI/MIDI\nmap.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 2021 08:48:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-25"}
