uler\nplatform as a `bag-of-tasks` algorithm for parallel and distributed workflow\nthough serial version has also been incorporated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 2021 14:48:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-08"}
